::Vamprah::

Vamprah continuing breathing as is she needed air, she
was stunning and she wasn'able  to defended herself,
discharge made her left, by a little time, her stasis
lock; she opened her golden eyes when she heard a
male-bot's voice.

She could  see at Devilduel, but she couldn't
understand nothing, with a breath, she only could said
"Darkfate..."

Other discharge of her necklance,(slighter than the
first) made her convulse. 

When it ended, Vamprah fell again in stasis lock and
her computer made a damage report "Beware, internnal
circuits couldnt stand other discharge of energy....
if discharges in level 10 continue, the spark turn
off...! Reparation class 10.67 is adviced."
